**LogSpiralTracker**  
**Description:**  
Analyzes log streams to detect spiraling error patterns, recursive chains, and escalation bursts.

```markdown
# LogSpiralTracker - Recursive Error Pattern Detector

LogSpiralTracker identifies repeating log structures that escalate or cycle through failure loops.

## Features
- Recursive pattern analysis  
- Escalation burst detection  
- CLI timeline filters

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LogSpiralTracker.git
cd LogSpiralTracker
python analyze.py
